snippet.description:

Dinesh Vijan and Maddock Films present #Ikkis, a true untold story of India‚Äôs youngest Param Vir Chakra awardee - Second Lieutenant Arun Khetarpal directed by Sriram Raghavan.

snippet.description:
Actually, I created this song long time ago but whenever I listen to it, I felt something incomplete and I thought that I could do lot of experiments to make this song more close towards the perfection. This year, finally, with the help, courage and push from my beloved people I am able to present you guys this beautiful masterpiece. 

‚ÄúTIHAR SONG‚Äù is an occasional song but if you dissect this creation musically and visually, you can find lots of interesting things, which will make your normal days; lightened and brighten up like Tihar. Jutta Talkiya 
Ek Ta Kala Yahi Thiya

Ghar Ni Halna Sakina Tin Tale
Marchhu Hola Swasni Kai Chinta Le 

Hamra Gau Ma Ko Rahich Aayako 
Kala Jutta Kalai Kot Layako 

Manche Pani Hawas Hawas Ti Ganako 
Kapal Pani Chya Kasto Banayako 

Kati Ramro Shirt Rahich Fiting 
Tai Shirt Ma Jumra Ko Meeting 

Natak Hera Kahi Na Bha Pari Ko 
Hero Mai Hu Yo Gau Bhari Ko 

Duita Tinta Chora Ko Ba Jastai 
Chasma Pani Magerai La Jastai  

Chasma Pani Lako Chhu Uk Ko 
Merai Lachhu Aru Lai Neu K Ko  

Dukha Paya Na Nidai Baser 
Hairan Bhayo Gau Ma Chor Paser  

Chaudhary Le Kata Chhau Bhai Bhanchhan 
Rajesh Hamal Kata Chhau Bhai Bhanchhan 

Khan Na Pako Kina Hun Palkine 
Ko Aayach Dat Matrai Talkine  

Jhin Ta Ta Tata Jhin Ta Ta 
Nani Taka Tani Nani Taka Tani 
Ululululu Myau Mayau 

You all gave so much love to our previous song makai bari daryam daryam and for that we are so grateful and we thank you from the bottom of our hearts! üíñ We‚Äôre back again with a brand new song, made purely to make you smile, laugh, and have a great time. This song comes straight from our hearts with only one intention: to entertain and spread joy and laughter. We have no intention to hurt or make fun of anyone. So just sit back, enjoy, and let‚Äôs laugh together!

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom‚ÄØFogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of‚ÄØthe day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.‚ÄØ‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 ‚Äì 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They‚Äôve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival‚Äôs canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like ‚ÄúBad Moon Rising,‚Äù ‚ÄúDown on the Corner,‚Äù ‚ÄúFortunate Son,‚Äù ‚ÄúHave You Ever Seen the Rain,‚Äù ‚ÄúProud Mary,‚Äù ‚ÄúBorn on the Bayou,‚Äù ‚ÄúTravelin‚Äô Band‚Äù and ‚ÄúUp Around the Bend‚Äù have been ingrained into pop culture ‚Äî not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America‚Äôs greatest rock ‚Äôn‚Äô roll band.

snippet.description:

Song: Panchhi Boley
Movie: Baahubali - The Beginning
Singers: M.M. Kreem & Palak Muchhal
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Composer: M.M. Kreem

Lyrics:
Panchhi Bole Hai Kya
Piya Sun Le Chalo
Pyaas Badhti Rahe Pyaar Hota Rahe
Aaj Dil Se Sadaa Aa Rahi Hai Suno
Ishq Jagta Rahe Waqt Sota Rahe

Itne Din Main Jiya Kya Jiya
Ab Toh Jeena Hai Tere Liye
Dil Ne Dil Se Yeh Vaada Kiya
Sau Janam Bhi Loon Tere Liye

Panchhi Bole Hai Kya
Piya Sun Le Chalo
Pyaas Badhti Rahe Pyaar Hota Rahe

Tu Kahe Toh Aasmaano Pe Likh Doon
Umar Bhar Ko Ab Toh Hona Judaa
Sab Likh Doon Aankhon Se
Aankhon Se Dil Pe Likh
Ishq Toh Pyaara Hai Pyaara Yaara

Itne Din Main Jiya Kya Jiya
Ab Toh Jeena Hai Tere Liye
Dil Ne Dil Se Yeh Vaada Kiya
Phir Janam Main Loon Tere Liye

Piya Sun Le Chalo
Pyaas Badhti Rahe Pyaar Hota Rahe

La Mere Naam Apni Shaamein Tu Kar De
Main Tujhe Doon Saare Palchhin Mere
Shaamein Teri Din Bhi Tere
Tujhko Diye Saare Lamhe
Le Ja Mujhko Aa Re Jogi Aa

snippet.title: NEW LEOPARD REWORK IN BLOX FRUITS!
snippet.description:
Today I reacted to the new leopard rework showcase. Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens. 

FOLTYN MERCH: https://foltyn.shop/

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/1177555...

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/foltynn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
